summary: Public anxiety
body:
Public anxiety

Tony x reader. Reader has public anxiety and Tony makes them feel better about it.

Warnings: fluff, anxiety

Fic:

“{Y/N}! Come on, we’re not getting any younger here… at least not yet.” Tony called out from the next room.


“Uh. Just a minute!” They called back as the slipped their new running shoes on and tied them tightly.


There was a pit sitting in their stomach. They loved doing things with Tony but, in the safety of their home. Being outside in the general public was the worst thing. All the people, was a heart attack waiting to happen.


I can do this. {Y/N} repeated over and over inside their head as they made their way to the front door. “Alright, let’s go.” They smiled as Tony took their hand leading them out the front door.


~~~~~


They walked through the park enjoying the fresh air. Tony kept giving them concerned glances every so often. Occasionally they’d stop so Tony could sign an autograph or take a picture. Every time {Y/N} stood off to the side waiting patiently for him to finish up.


“What’s with you today?” Tony inquired as pulled them off to the side of the path.


“Nothing.” They mutters looking down.


Tony lifted their head up to look at him. He had a gentle smile on his face. “It’s not nothing. Normally your all over me. What’s different?”


“Oh.” {Y/N} muttered as they fidgeted with their coat. “I thought it was annoying be hanging on you all the time and a lot of your fans don’t like it. They call me clingy.. I just thought maybe you didn’t like it either.”


Tony let let out a bellowing laugh as he pulled them in close. “I love you being all clingy. I know being in public give you major anxiety so I love when your pressed against me when we go for walks or shopping. Don’t let those fools make you doubt yourself or us. I love you just the way you are.”

summary: Iron Fist Week Day 2 - Favorite Romantic Ship: Colleen/Colleen Wow, Day one went great a lot of people liked my fic and I would...
caption:
Iron Fist Week Day 2 - Favorite Romantic Ship: Colleen/Colleen

Wow, Day one went great a lot of people liked my fic and I would like to thank all who did. Now for day two, which is post about your favorite Iron Fist romantic ship. Well, that’s where we run into a problem I really don’t ship anyone on that show or even in the comics. I guess that if I did ship someone it would have to be Colleen with herself. Mostly because I think that she needs some time to figure out who she is independent of her relationship with Danny and her relationship with the Hand. And we as a audience need to see her do that and kick serious ASS while doing it. I’ve been thinking this since the very beginning of the show and I physically gag every time I see Danny and Colleen go all googly eyes over each other. I also hated that in show they made her a descendant of Wu Ao-Shi because that totally disregards her own separate and awesome backstory and links her to Danny’s indefinitely. So I believe that Colleen needed to break up with Danny so that way she could find out who she is as a person and reconcile her past with herself. She needs to love herself before she can love anyone else.

Thank you for reading my rant

kkbobay
